<p source="SHANGBO.BANGRENBUCHENG 9.58.1 (STRIPS 1-2A) MACHENGYUAN 9: 242-243 TR. MARCO CABOARA"><pb xml:id="KR2p0086_tls_001-1a" ed="tls" n="001-1a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0086_tls_001-1a.1">[...] 子乎?</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0086_tls_001-1a.2">故不以至命.</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0086_tls_001-1a.3">侵（箴?）尹曰：</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0086_tls_001-1a.4">“天加訛（禍）於楚邦，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0086_tls_001-1a.5">吾君盪出,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0086_tls_001-1a.6">威視 (?) [...] 【1】</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0086_tls_001-1a.7">亡名焉</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0086_tls_001-1a.8">是故弗知也. 【2A】</seg></p>

<p source="SHANGBO.BANGRENBUCHENG 9.58.2 (STRIPS 2B-3) MACHENGYUAN 9: 243-245 TR. MARCO CABOARA"><pb xml:id="KR2p0086_tls_001-2a" ed="tls" n="001-2a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0086_tls_001-2a.1">[...] 祓天之女.</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0086_tls_001-2a.2">就昭王之亡，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0086_tls_001-2a.3">要 (遇?）王於隨待，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0086_tls_001-2a.4">戰於澨，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0086_tls_001-2a.5">戰於津，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0086_tls_001-2a.6">戰於長【2B】</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0086_tls_001-2a.7">[...] 曲陶，</seg></p>

<p source="SHANGBO.BANGRENBUCHENG 9.58.3 (STRIPS 3-4) MACHENGYUAN 9: 245-247 TR. MARCO CABOARA"><pb xml:id="KR2p0086_tls_001-3a" ed="tls" n="001-3a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0086_tls_001-3a.1">三戰而三止，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0086_tls_001-3a.2">而邦人不稱勇焉.</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0086_tls_001-3a.3">就復邦之後,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0086_tls_001-3a.4">蓋冠爲王獲,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0086_tls_001-3a.5">而邦人【3】不稱美焉.</seg></p>

<p source="SHANGBO.BANGRENBUCHENG 9.58.4 (STRIP 4) MACHENGYUAN 9: 247 TR. MARCO CABOARA"><pb xml:id="KR2p0086_tls_001-4a" ed="tls" n="001-4a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0086_tls_001-4a.1">就白公之禍，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0086_tls_001-4a.2">聞令尹, 司馬既死，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0086_tls_001-4a.3">將適郢.</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0086_tls_001-4a.4">葉之諸老皆諫曰：</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0086_tls_001-4a.5">“不可，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0086_tls_001-4a.6">必以師.”</seg></p>

<p source="SHANGBO.BANGRENBUCHENG 9.58.5 (STRIPS 4-5) MACHENGYUAN 9: 247-250 TR. MARCO CABOARA"><pb xml:id="KR2p0086_tls_001-5a" ed="tls" n="001-5a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0086_tls_001-5a.1">葉【4】公子高曰：</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0086_tls_001-5a.2">“不得王，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0086_tls_001-5a.3">將必死，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0086_tls_001-5a.4">何以師爲?”</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0086_tls_001-5a.5">乃乘馹車五乘，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0086_tls_001-5a.6">遂適郢.</seg></p>

<p source="SHANGBO.BANGRENBUCHENG 9.58.6 (STRIPS 5-7) MACHENGYUAN 9: 250-251 TR. MARCO CABOARA"><pb xml:id="KR2p0086_tls_001-6a" ed="tls" n="001-6a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0086_tls_001-6a.1">至, 未得王，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0086_tls_001-6a.2">昭夫人謂葉公【5】子高：</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0086_tls_001-6a.3">“先君之子聚在外 [...]【6】</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0086_tls_001-6a.4">君之言過，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0086_tls_001-6a.5">昔周(?)盍擇而立之，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0086_tls_001-6a.6">邦既有王，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0086_tls_001-6a.7">毋亦(?) 勸乎?</seg></p>

<p source="SHANGBO.BANGRENBUCHENG 9.58.7 (STRIPS 7-8) MACHENGYUAN 9: 252-253 TR. MARCO CABOARA"><pb xml:id="KR2p0086_tls_001-7a" ed="tls" n="001-7a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0086_tls_001-7a.1">葉公子高曰：</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0086_tls_001-7a.2">“万(?)千君[㫃旱（幹?）]，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0086_tls_001-7a.3">何施獻【7】之惑也，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0086_tls_001-7a.4">而并是二者以邦君，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0086_tls_001-7a.5">君猶小之，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0086_tls_001-7a.6">一懼君之不終世,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0086_tls_001-7a.7">保邦.</seg></p>

<p source="SHANGBO.BANGRENBUCHENG 9.58.8 (STRIPS 8-9) MACHENGYUAN 9: 253-254 TR. MARCO CABOARA"><pb xml:id="KR2p0086_tls_001-8a" ed="tls" n="001-8a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0086_tls_001-8a.1">既言,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0086_tls_001-8a.2">乃服固祝而止之.</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0086_tls_001-8a.3">蔡【8】大祝止，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0086_tls_001-8a.4">須邦君加冠冕爲服,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0086_tls_001-8a.5">出就蔡大祝踊,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0086_tls_001-8a.6">二拜頓首曰：</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0086_tls_001-8a.7">“今日踊,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0086_tls_001-8a.8">既失邦,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0086_tls_001-8a.9">或得之.”</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0086_tls_001-8a.10">蔡大 [...]【9】</seg></p>

<p source="SHANGBO.BANGRENBUCHENG 9.58.9 (STRIPS 11) MACHENGYUAN 9: 257 TR. MARCO CABOARA"><pb xml:id="KR2p0086_tls_001-9a" ed="tls" n="001-9a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0086_tls_001-9a.1">寍禍.</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0086_tls_001-9a.2">賞之以西廣田百畛，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0086_tls_001-9a.3">辭曰：</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0086_tls_001-9a.4">“君王諍臣之請命，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0086_tls_001-9a.5">未嘗不許.”</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0086_tls_001-9a.6">辭不受賞.</seg></p>

<p source="SHANGBO.BANGRENBUCHENG 9.58.10 (STRIPS 11, 12, 10) MACHENGYUAN 9: 257-258, 256 TR. MARCO CABOARA"><pb xml:id="KR2p0086_tls_001-10a" ed="tls" n="001-10a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0086_tls_001-10a.1">命之為令【11】尹,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0086_tls_001-10a.2">辭.</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0086_tls_001-10a.3">命之為司馬,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0086_tls_001-10a.4">辭,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0086_tls_001-10a.5">曰：saying:</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0086_tls_001-10a.6">"以葉之遠，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0086_tls_001-10a.7">不可畜也."</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0086_tls_001-10a.8">焉假為司馬，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0086_tls_001-10a.9">不取其實，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0086_tls_001-10a.10">而邦人不稱榮【12】焉.</seg></p>

<p source="SHANGBO.BANGRENBUCHENG 9.58.11 (STRIPS 10, 13) MACHENGYUAN 9: 256, 259 TR. MARCO CABOARA"><pb xml:id="KR2p0086_tls_001-11a" ed="tls" n="001-11a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0086_tls_001-11a.1">就王之長也，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0086_tls_001-11a.2">賞之以焚域百畛，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0086_tls_001-11a.3">故為葉連囂與蔡樂尹，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0086_tls_001-11a.4">而邦人不稱貪焉.</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0086_tls_001-11a.5">臣焉 [...]【10】</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0086_tls_001-11a.6">吾豈敢以爾亂邦?”【13】</seg></p>

</div>
